title.narrative: To get to Zero Indigenous case by 2022 and sustain it thereafter to achieve Malaria elimination by 2025

description.narrative: Nepal - Malaria - Save the Children Federation, Inc. - STC HQ. This program has the following goals: To achieve zero death due to malaria by 2015 and sustain it thereafter. To reduce the incidence of indigenous malaria cases by 90% of 2012 levels by 2018. Number of VDCs having indigenous malaria cases by 70% of 2012 levels by 2018. To receive WHO certification of malaria free status by 2025.. The objectives of this program are: To strengthen strategic information for decision making towards malaria elimination. To further reduce malaria transmission and eliminate the foci. To improve quality of and access to early diagnosis and effective treatment of malaria. To sustain support from the political leadership and the communities towards malaria elimination. To strengthens programmatic technical and managerial capacities towards malaria elimination
